====
Sejam latexmath:[$u=(1,2,3,4)$ e $v=(6,7,-1,3)$]. Então
[latexmath]
++++
\[
\begin{array}{rcl}
u+v &=& (1,2,3,4) +  (6,7,-1,3) = (1+6, 2+7, 3+(-1), 4+3) = (7,9,2,7) \\
-2u &=&  -2 (1,2,3,4) =  (-2(1), -2(2), -2(3), -2(4))= (-2,-4, -6, -8)  \\
3u-4v &=& 3(1,2,3,4) - 4(6,7,-1,3)\\
      &=& (3(1),3(2),3(3),3(4)) + ((-4)6,(-4)7,(-4)(-1),(-4)3)\\
&=& (3,6,9,12)+ (-24,-28, 4, -12)\\
